Summary

Dataset: Malawi

Outcome: MDAT motor at Midline (fm20 - fm43)

Comparison variable: age (3, 4)

Items with no variance: none

Items with no variance within levels of comparison variable: none

Bias detection method: logistic using Rest Scores

Total number of biased items: 9 out of 21

Type of item bias: non-uniform
